  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium heat.",
    "Add almonds and sauté until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in garlic and chili flakes; cook for another minute until fragrant.",
    "Add chickpeas to the pan. Season with salt and pepper.",
    "Finally, add capers and stir well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes to let flavors meld together."
